track_notes: Parked at the roadside as advised by G4ERP and a straightforward walk from there.

Total time (including ops): 1h. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Longridge Fell Linear from Southwest. Jul 2023.

track_notes: Alternative route from the south. Park near forest at Old Clitheroe Rd., follow wide forest track until clearing with the stone steps. Turn towards forest and follow narrow rocky path. Cross through dense forest. At the end of the path you should find stone wall. Follow wall in West direction towards the trig point.
